{"id":4707,"date":"2014-10-13T08:52:21","date_gmt":"2014-10-13T08:52:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/?p=4707"},"modified":"2016-04-25T07:36:31","modified_gmt":"2016-04-25T07:36:31","slug":"tfs-update-4-ctp-2-features-and-installation","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/2014\/10\/13\/tfs-update-4-ctp-2-features-and-installation\/","title":{"rendered":"TFS Update 4 CTP 2 Features and installation"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Microsoft released Visual Studio 2013 Update 4 Community Technology Preview 2 (CTP 2) on September 22, 2014, it includes some new features and bug fixes.<\/p>\n<p>For more information about this release visit the KB: <a href=\"https:\/\/support2.microsoft.com\/kb\/2994375\">https:\/\/support2.microsoft.com\/kb\/2994375<\/a><\/p>\n<p>This post has main 2 sections:<\/p>\n<p><strong>Team Foundation Server Features<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Web Access can return directly to query results from a detailed view of the query by using a context menu.<\/li>\n<li>Web Access can generate an email directly from the work item view by using a new toolbar command.<\/li>\n<li>Web Access has a full-screen option to view query results.<\/li>\n<li>The free Stakeholder license provides access to the project home page from which Stakeholders can view the backlog, edit items, run work item queries, and many other operations.<\/li>\n<li>Agile teams can have up to 999 work items in the first or last column of the Kanban board.<\/li>\n<li>Web Access now opens a work item in a new window or tab.<\/li>\n<li>You can maximize (or full screen) fields for quick readability when the rich text editor does not have enough space.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Installation and configuration<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>What you need to know before you install<\/li>\n<li>How to install and configure.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Team Foundation Server Features<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>The following is the walk through video<br \/>\n[youtube=&#8221;http:\/\/youtu.be\/gByYtNfo26g&#8221;]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Web Access can return directly to query results from a detailed view of the query by using a context menu.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>In the Team Web Access if you run a query and open a work-item from the query result, you can get back to the query result from the work-item context menu on the top-right.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/2014\/10\/13\/tfs-update-4-ctp-2-features-and-installation\/9-25-2014-5-56-27-pm\/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-4711\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-4711\" src=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-5-56-27-pm.png?w=660\" alt=\"9-25-2014 5-56-27 PM\" width=\"660\" height=\"380\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-5-56-27-pm.png 1115w, https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-5-56-27-pm-300x173.png 300w, https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-5-56-27-pm-768x443.png 768w, https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-5-56-27-pm-1024x591.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/2014\/10\/13\/tfs-update-4-ctp-2-features-and-installation\/9-25-2014-5-58-17-pm\/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-4712\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-4712\" src=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-5-58-17-pm.png?w=660\" alt=\"9-25-2014 5-58-17 PM\" width=\"660\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-5-58-17-pm.png 1034w, https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-5-58-17-pm-300x167.png 300w, https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-5-58-17-pm-768x428.png 768w, https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-5-58-17-pm-1024x570.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Web Access can generate an email directly from the work item view by using a new toolbar command.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>In the previous update 3, you can send email from the context menu only but now you can send email from the work-item tool bar.<br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/image005.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-4724\" src=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/image005.png?w=660\" alt=\"image005\" width=\"660\" height=\"448\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/image005.png 752w, https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/image005-300x204.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" \/><br \/>\n<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/2014\/10\/13\/tfs-update-4-ctp-2-features-and-installation\/9-25-2014-6-29-13-pm\/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-4713\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-4713\" src=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-6-29-13-pm.png?w=660\" alt=\"9-25-2014 6-29-13 PM\" width=\"660\" height=\"493\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-6-29-13-pm.png 801w, https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-6-29-13-pm-300x224.png 300w, https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/9-25-2014-6-29-13-pm-768x574.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Web Access has a full-screen option to view query results.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Now you can full-screen for the query result for better readability<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/2014\/10\/13\/tfs-update-4-ctp-2-features-and-installation\/9-25-2014-6-32-19-pm\/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-4714\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decod